    {
      "id": "standard_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "This car is in fair condition. It runs and drives, but shows noticeable wear both mechanically and cosmetically. Expect some maintenance needs in the near term. The exterior has visible scratches and minor dents, and the interior shows moderate wear. It is functional for daily use but is not without its issues.",
